momma raised a hustler and the struggle made a beast

lyrics.text:
I gotta run it up

Momma raised a hustler and the struggle made a beast 
I put shit in motion and it comeback in my sleep 
You ain't nothing like me and I know youll never be 
Ain't been in the jungle you ain't seen the shit I seen
All these rappers actors pillow talk between the sheets
Read between the lines cannot take the heat 
Made it thru the drought and now I water my whole team
I can't take partial love I'm needing the whole thing 

I gotta run it up

Momma still working 2 jobs
That's my motivation
Both my siblings tryna find a way 
That's my motivation 
Grandma walk to work 
Everyday that's motivation
Until the whole family straight 
That's my motivation

Lately I by praying fasting tryna practice patience
Turned in applications waiting faith within my greatness 
Really it's a journey and my wins are for they takin 
Wait they for the claiming 
That's where I'm mistaken 
Thinking they can take it
Over time my 9 to 5 is 25 / 8
And i gotta run it up 
Rest is still a must 
I just don't know how when them bills pillin up kids growing up 
Thinkin what the fuck 

I can't believe what I've seen 
How u gone block someone blessing then cap like u with us and want everybody to eat
How u gone say that you hear for the gang and then leave when it's wicked and cold in the streets 
Honestly I keep it cool because all of the doubt and hate really motivate me 
Causally eating these beats and I clear any bitch I know thats that's really tea 
They don't want me on a feature I'm really a spitter they might as well stop and just sing 
I'm out here getting this paper I'm getting the chicken and lettuce it come with the cheese
She wanna fuck cuz I'm cool I don't make up the rules I'm just cooling and keeping it P
I Got this shit off the muscle the hustle 
My nigga ain't no body fucking with me 
all that tussle and shuffle not really my thing for real but do as you please 
Who really matching my energy 
Who really matching my ethic
Point em out quickly and tell em I'm with it
I came from bottom I gotta go get it fr 

i gotta run it up

Me and all my gang WGMI
